  "description": "A wide-angle nighttime landscape photograph showing a dark, rocky foreground leading to distant, silhouetted mountains under a vibrant, star-filled sky. The sky is a deep indigo and blue, densely populated with numerous stars, creating a sense of vastness and cosmic scale. A prominent streak of the Milky Way galaxy arcs across the upper portion of the frame, its stars appearing as a concentrated band of light. The foreground consists of dark, uneven terrain covered with rocks and sparse vegetation. The mountains are low and jagged, their shapes barely distinguishable against the night sky. The overall composition evokes a sense of remote wilderness and natural beauty.",
